value.name: Wall Guards & Crash Rails | Wall Protection | Wallprotex
value.snippet: The retainer wall guard (or crash rail) utilizes three layers of impact absorption to provide superior long-term wall protection. The aluminum retainer and vinyl impact absorber are concealed by a replaceable, snap-on vinyl cover, uniquely combining the benefits of greater visual appeal and the increased durability necessary for high-impact and high traffic environments like medical and hospitality.

value.name: Abatis - Wikipedia
value.snippet: An abatis, abattis, or abbattis is a field fortification consisting of an obstacle formed (in the modern era) of the branches of trees laid in a row, with the sharpened tops directed outwards, towards the enemy. The trees are usually interlaced or tied with wire. Abatis are used alone or in combination with wire entanglements and other obstacles.
